 entwined.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2020) 0aEnvironmental geology. 0aGlobal environmental change. 0aNaturexEffect of human beings on. 0aPaleoecologyyHolocene. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook-Package 2016z978311066754708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press eBook-Package 2016-2018z978311063539308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCal Press eBook Package 2014-2016z978311065748740uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520964334423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520964334.jpg  a978-3-11-063539-3  UC Press eBook-Package 2016-2018c2016d2018  a978-3-11-065748-7  UCal Press eBook Package 2014-2016c2014d2016  a978-3-11-066754-7  UC Press eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles